data.description: POOL home at the end of a Cul-De-Sac with a large gated back yard!  This home has plenty of storage and so much potential!  Detached garage as well as a workshop AND additional storage room.  There is also a very large FL/Flex room that could be anything you wish such as... an Office, a Sun room, Play room or Gym!  Just a few minutes from lots of shopping, restaurants and downtown Ft Myers!
